UsePAM no
HostbasedAuthentication no
IgnoreUserKnownHosts yes
ListenAddress {{listen_ip}}
HostKey {{parent_dir}}/ca_host_key

MaxAuthTries 99999
MaxSessions 99999
MaxStartups 99999
